          <div class="photo-wrapper">
            <img src="/images/rudra-rand-fishkin.jpeg" alt="Rudra Kasturi with Rand Fishkin, founder of Moz and SparkToro" />
            <div class="photo-overlay">
              <span class="photo-tag">MozCon</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="photo-info">
            <h3>With Rand Fishkin</h3>
            <p>Founder of Moz & SparkToro. The godfather of modern SEO.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="photo-card">
          <div class="photo-wrapper">
            <img src="/images/rudra-matt.jpeg" alt="Rudra Kasturi with Matt Cutts, former head of Google Webspam" />
            <div class="photo-overlay">
              <span class="photo-tag">Google</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="photo-info">
            <h3>With Matt Cutts</h3>
            <p>Former Head of Google Webspam. The legend who shaped search quality.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="photo-card">
          <div class="photo-wrapper">
            <img src="/images/rudra-john.jpeg" alt="Rudra Kasturi with John Mueller, Google Search Advocate" />
            <div class="photo-overlay">
              <span class="photo-tag">Google Search</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="photo-info">
            <h3>With John Mueller</h3>
            <p>Google's Senior Search Analyst & Search Advocate. The voice of Google Search.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="photo-card">
          <div class="photo-wrapper">
            <img src="/images/farmer-rudra.jpeg" alt="Rudra Kasturi on his farm" />
            <div class="photo-overlay">
              <span class="photo-tag">The Farm Life</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="photo-info">
            <h3>Beyond the Boardroom</h3>
            <p>When not scaling businesses, farming keeps things real. Patience, soil, and long games.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Section -->
  <section class="section about-premium" id="about">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-layout">
        <div class="about-content">
          <div class="about-badge">About</div>
          <h2 class="about-headline">What I <span class="gradient-text">Actually Do</span></h2>
          <p class="about-lead">
            I've spent two decades at the intersection of search, AI, and growth, as the person accountable for results.
          </p>
          <p>
            From building <strong>Amazon India's</strong> organic search from scratch to scaling
            <strong>Times Group</strong> properties to category-leading positions, to owning growth
            at <strong>BYJU's</strong>, the mandate has always been the same: identify the ceiling, then remove it.
          </p>
          <p>
            I also advise companies including <strong>Tencent</strong>, <strong>CRED</strong>,
            <strong>Antler India</strong>, <strong>Haptik</strong>, and
            <strong>Tasva (Aditya Birla Group)</strong>, across stages from Series A to enterprise scale.
          </p>
          <p>
            And I teach. Because the next generation doesn't need theory. It needs operators.
          </p>

          <!-- Infographic Strip -->
          <div class="infographic-strip">
            <div class="infographic-item">
              <div class="infographic-bar" style="--bar-width: 95%">
                <span class="infographic-label">Search & SEO</span>
                <span class="infographic-value">22 yrs</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="infographic-item">
              <div class="infographic-bar" style="--bar-width: 65%">
                <span class="infographic-label">AI & ML Strategy</span>
                <span class="infographic-value">3 yrs</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="infographic-item">
              <div class="infographic-bar" style="--bar-width: 90%">
                <span class="infographic-label">Growth & Scale</span>
                <span class="infographic-value">500M+ users</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="infographic-item">
              <div class="infographic-bar" style="--bar-width: 75%">
                <span class="infographic-label">Advisory & Consulting</span>
                <span class="infographic-value">15+ brands</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="infographic-item">
              <div class="infographic-bar" style="--bar-width: 70%">
                <span class="infographic-label">Teaching & EdTech</span>
                <span class="infographic-value">15K+ students</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-highlights">
          <div class="highlight-card">
            <div class="highlight-icon">&#9733;</div>
            <h4>Operator, Not Advisor</h4>
            <p>CSO, SVP, and VP roles at companies with hundreds of millions of users. The decisions were mine to make and mine to live with.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="highlight-card">
            <div class="highlight-icon">&#9775;</div>
            <h4>Search & AI, Since the Beginning</h4>
            <p>From early SEO infrastructure at Amazon and Yahoo to AI strategy at India Today. This has been the work for twenty years.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="highlight-card">
            <div class="highlight-icon">&#9889;</div>
            <h4>500M+ Users, Real Platforms</h4>
            <p>Media, edtech, e-commerce, and entertainment at scale.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="highlight-card">
            <div class="highlight-icon">&#127758;</div>
