  </section>

  <!-- Founder Section -->
  <section class="section founder-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title text-center">Founder & Builder</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle text-center">Building companies that create real impact</p>
      <div class="founder-grid">
        <a href="https://aividhyarthi.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="founder-card">
          <div class="founder-logo-text">AIVidhyaRthi</div>
          <div class="founder-tagline">Teaching AI to Every Student in Their Own Language</div>
          <p>We bring AI education to students and teachers in tier 2 &amp; tier 3 cities across India — empowering them to build projects, create startups, and shape their future with cutting-edge AI tools.</p>
          <div class="founder-stats-row">
            <div class="founder-stat"><strong>14,122</strong><span>Students Trained</span></div>
            <div class="founder-stat"><strong>50+</strong><span>Cities Reached</span></div>
            <div class="founder-stat"><strong>382</strong><span>Teachers Empowered</span></div>
          </div>
          <span class="founder-link">aividhyarthi.org &rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://appstudiox.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="founder-card">
          <div class="founder-logo-text">AppStudioX</div>
          <div class="founder-tagline">Dominate Search. Build Authority. Drive Real Growth.</div>
          <p>Full-service digital growth agency trusted by India's most iconic brands — from media giants to D2C disruptors. We don't just rank you. We make you the authority your audience turns to first.</p>
          <span class="founder-link">appstudiox.com &rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://hermidlife.com.au" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="founder-card">
          <div class="founder-logo-text">HerMidLife</div>
          <div class="founder-tagline">Perimenopause care that actually understands you</div>
          <p>Because "it's just stress" was never the answer. Expert-led symptom tracking, telehealth with specialist practitioners, and personalised ongoing support — designed for the millions of Australian women navigating perimenopause and menopause.</p>
          <span class="founder-link">hermidlife.com.au &rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/the-vault" class="founder-card">
          <div class="founder-logo-text">The Vault</div>
          <div class="founder-tagline">A 2am companion for men who need to be heard</div>
          <p>Anonymous, private, judgment-free. A space where men can say what's on their mind — at 2am or any time. No therapy. No fixing. Just someone (AI) who listens without judging.</p>
          <span class="founder-link">Open The Vault &rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <div class="founder-card founder-card-accent">
          <div class="founder-logo-text">Rudra Kasturi Inc.</div>
          <p>Strategic consulting for enterprises and startups. From search to AI, zero to scale.</p>
          <span class="founder-link">Consulting &amp; Advisory</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Farmer Section -->
  <section class="section farmer-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="farmer-layout">
        <div class="farmer-image-wrapper">
          <img src="/images/farmer-rudra.jpeg" alt="Rudra Kasturi on his farm" class="farmer-image" />
        </div>
        <div class="farmer-content">
          <h2 class="section-title">Beyond the Boardroom</h2>
          <p class="farmer-lead">When I'm not working, I'm on the farm.</p>
          <p>
            No dashboards. No decks. Just time, soil, and patience.
          </p>
          <p>
